<div class="sectbreak"><h2>Plan Your Trip</h2></div>

<div class="container">
  <section class="welcome-section">
    <h1><%= message %></h1>
    <p>Plan smarter with Trip Tuner. Just enter your destination, travel dates, budget, and preferences â€” and get a personalized,
